rows.label: tlk45300451_03_msg0001
rows.name: Thanks for what you did before.

rows.label: tlk45300451_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Being able to see Musubi
again, it really helped
ease my heart a little.

rows.label: tlk45300451_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Me and my sister didn't become
Drivers because our old man
warned us against it.

rows.label: tlk45300451_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm just glad she found a good
Driver to work for now that he's
gone. That's what he'd have wanted.

rows.label: tlk45300451_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I probably don't need to
tell you this, but...take
good care of Musubi, yeah?
